text: Louis Albert (28 May 1898 - 30 January 1951) was a French ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1924 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1898 births Category:1951 deaths Category:French male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of France Category:Ski jumpers at the 1924 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
